%F A397351 a(n) = A397350(2*n-1, n-1) for n >= 1.
%F A397351 a(n) = (2*n-1)! * [x^(2*n-1)*y^(n-1)] F(x,y), where F(x,y) is the e.g.f. of triangle A397350 satisfying Sum_{n>=0} y^n * (F(x,y)^n - x)^n / n! = 1.
